IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Nicole Rae SEWARD and Adam Clark Seward Upon the Petition of Nicole Rae Seward, Petitioner-Appellant, And Concerning Adam Clark Seward, Respondent-Appellee. No. 18-1690 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 1, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Nicole Seward appeals the modification of the visitation and child support provisions of the dissolution decree. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
